data.description: Rare opportunity in esteemed Highland Trails!  This true 4 bed + study, 2.5 bath, 3 car garage home with a welcoming private pool, and a half acre+ (MOL) lot, is tucked down a quiet double cul-de-sac and been beautifully maintained!  MIL floor plan has the spacious primary bedroom on one side and secondary bedrooms on the other with central living spaces (kitchen/study/dining/den).  Beautifully updated countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms!  Large covered back patio with extended concrete for added outdoor living.  Unique neighborhood with an active HOA, community events, playground, clubhouse, walking trails, and community pool.
